  "governance_notes": "All children preserve Stage 1 semantics and Stage 2 interfaces exactly. Resource fields are derived solely from internal_leaf_accesses. ParseCommand has no data store accesses, so its global_vars and data_operations are empty. PlaceOrder, CancelOrder, and TrackOrder each have global_vars and data_operations synchronized with their internal_leaf_accesses. No exceptions needed.",
